        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[关于组织开展“全民国家安全教育”主题团日活动的通知]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[关于组织开展“全民国家安全教育”主题团日活动的通知]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/11/120716</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/11/120716</guid>
            <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 06:54:22 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded>&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;punctuation-wrap:simple&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;为牢固树立和践行总体国家安全观，在第十个全民国家安全教育日来临之际，航天学院组织开展&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;“全民国家安全教育”主题团日活动。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;punctuation-wrap:simple&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;黑体&quot;&gt;一、面向对象&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;punctuation-wrap:simple&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;航天学院全体团支部&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;punctuation-wrap:simple&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;黑体&quot;&gt;二、活动时间&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;punctuation-wrap:simple&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;2025&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;年&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;4&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;月&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;11&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;日—&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;15&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;日&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;punctuation-wrap:simple&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;黑体&quot;&gt;三、活动形式&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;punctuation-wrap:simple&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;各团支部可围绕宪法、国家安全法、网络安全法和反间谍法等法律法规，自行组织开展&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;“全民国家安全教育”主题团日活动。可采取参观黑龙江省国家安全教育实践基地、邀请国家安全教育名师走进党团支部、国家安全教育主题知识问答等形式。要求活动注重实效，避免形式化，确保支部成员全员参与。活动结束后，各团支部需于&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;4&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;月&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;15&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;日&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;17:00&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;前填写表单，按照《附件&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;1&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;：航天学院&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;XXX&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;团支部“全民国家安全教育”主题团日活动总结》格式提交一份活动总结，由学院统一审核后择优在“今日哈工大”平台宣传报道。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;方正仿宋简体&quot;&gt;表单链接：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://hitsa-sw.mikecrm.com/7YOKgoi&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;15&quot; style=&quot;text-underline:single&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;https://hitsa-sw.mikecrm.com/7YOKgoi&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【Hi-Talk】国别主题特色周第二期预告——泰国]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【Hi-Talk】国别主题特色周第二期预告——泰国]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/11/120711</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/11/120711</guid>
            <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 06:54:24 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;亲爱的同学们：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; 你是否想在校园里就能体验泰国的多元文化？是否想品尝地道的泰国美食，欣赏曼妙的泰国舞蹈，体验泰国传统游戏，或是学习几句地道的泰语以及世界上最长的城市名字？机会来了！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Dear students,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Would you like to experience Thailand&apos;s vibrant and diverse culture without leaving campus? Taste authentic Thai dishes, enjoy graceful traditional dances, play fun Thai games, and learn a few basic Thai phrases — including the full ceremonial name of Bangkok, the longest city name in the world? Now&apos;s your chance!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; 泰国文化展位即将开启，欢迎你走进热情好客的“微笑之国”，沉浸在宋干节的欢乐中，开启一段奇妙的文化探索之旅！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The Thailand Culture Booth will be opening soon! Step into the Land of Smiles, celebrate Songkran Festival, and dive into a heartwarming cultural journey full of joy and discovery!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;活动亮点 | Event Highlights&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;美食品尝：舌尖上的泰国&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Thai Food Tasting: A Taste of Thailand&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• ลาบไก่（辣味鸡肉拌菜 | Spicy Chicken Salad &quot;Larb Gai&quot;）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• กะเพราะไก่（打抛鸡饭 | Stir-fried Basil Chicken &quot;Pad Kra Pao&quot;）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;传统舞蹈与音乐表演&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Traditional Thai Dance &amp;amp; Music&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;泰国学生将身着传统服饰，为大家带来优雅的泰国舞蹈。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Thai students will dress in traditional Thai outfits and perform graceful cultural dances.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;语言互动：你好，泰国！&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Language Interaction: Hello Thailand!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• 学习常用泰语： &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• “你好” (สวัสดีค่ะ / ครับ Sawasdee ka/krap)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• “谢谢” (ขอบคุณค่ะ / ครับ Khob Khun ka/krap)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• 学习曼谷的全名——被吉尼斯世界记录认证为世界上最长的城市名称 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• Learn the full ceremonial name of Bangkok, the longest city name in the world!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;泰国文化与传统问候礼仪“合十礼”（Wai）&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Thai Culture &amp;amp; the Traditional Greeting – &quot;Wai&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;了解泰国不同地区文化特色，体验泰国人以微笑与“Wai”传达的热情好客。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Explore Thailand’s regional culture and the warmth of Thai hospitality through the traditional &quot;Wai&quot; greeting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; 无论你是热爱品尝美食、喜爱东南亚文化，还是想寻找一次特别的体验，泰国文化展位都能满足你的期待！从香辣可口的泰式料理，到丰富多彩的传统节日，还有充满智慧的泰式&lt;/span&gt;Massage&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;和手工艺，每一个角落都充满惊喜与魅力。快来一起感受泰国的微笑、热情与独特文化，让我们带你开启一段精彩的泰国文化之旅！国别主题特色周——泰国文化展位，等你来发现！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Whether you’re a food lover, a Southeast Asian culture enthusiast, or simply looking for a unique experience — the &lt;b&gt;Thailand Cultural Booth&lt;/b&gt; has something special for you! From flavorful Thai dishes and colorful traditional festivals to the art of Thai massage and local handicrafts, every corner offers a taste of Thailand’s charm. Come and feel the warmth, smiles, and vibrant spirit of Thai culture. Let us take you on a memorable cultural journey! Join us at the &lt;b&gt;Country-Specific Themed Feature Week&lt;/b&gt; – Thailand Booth and discover the magic of Thailand!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;活动详情 | Event Details&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• 时间 | Time: 04月14日 - 04月18日 | April 14 - April 18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• 地点 | Venue: A03公寓国际教育学院暖廊 (Warm Corridor of A03 Apartment, CIE)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;• 参与方式 | Participation: 欢迎所有同学参加！(All students are welcome!)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;活动时间安排 | Event Schedule&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 11px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;第一天&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot; xml:lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2025-04-14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;（15:00-16:00）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;泰国传统游戏&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;1.捡豆子游戏&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;2.橡胶跳跃游戏&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;3.蛇吃尾巴游戏&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Day 1&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2025-04-14 (15:00–&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;16:00)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Traditional Thai Games&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:36.0pt&quot;&gt;1.The “Pick-up Beans” Game&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:36.0pt&quot;&gt;2.Rubber Band Jumping Game&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:36.0pt&quot;&gt;3.“Snake Tail Chase” Game&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;第二天&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;2025-04-15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;（15:00-16:00）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:49.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;欢迎参加宋干节活动&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;一起来了解充满温馨与欢乐的泰国传统新年——宋干节，并参与有趣的传统活动，例如唱宋干节歌曲、互相抹粉，共度一个充满泰式风情的快乐时光！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Day 2&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2025-04-15 (15:00–&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;16:00)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Join Us for the Songkran Festival!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Discover the warm and joyful Thai New Year tradition—Songkran—and take part in fun activities like singing Songkran songs and applying scented powder in a festive Thai-style atmosphere.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;第三天&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;2025-04-16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;（15:00-16:00）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;学习泰语&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:48.0pt&quot;&gt;学习如何用泰语给自己起名字!玩一个由日常词汇组成的闪卡游戏比如Sawatdi (泰语的你好)!学习日常生活中的简单用语！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Day 3&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2025-04-16 (15:00&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;–&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;16:00)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Learn Thai&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Learn how to name yourself in Thai language! Play a flashcard game that consists of daily vocabulary eg. Sawatdi (hello in Thai). Study the simple phrases that are used in real-life situations!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;第四天&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;2025-04-17&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;（15:00-16:00）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;欢迎品尝受欢迎的泰国美食&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;泰国菜以其美味和独特风味而闻名，如打抛（泰式炒肉末）、辣拌（拉布）等，深受泰国人及世界各地人们的喜爱。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;今天大家将有机会亲自品尝地道的泰国美食！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Day &lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;4&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2025-04-17 (15:00&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;–&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;16:00)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Come Taste Popular Thai Dishes!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Thai cuisine is known for its delicious flavors and unique character. Dishes like Pad Kra Pao (stir-fried basil with meat) and Larb (spicy salad) are loved both in Thailand and around the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Today, you’ll get the chance to enjoy authentic Thai food firsthand!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;第五天&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;2025-04-18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing:.4pt&quot;&gt;（15:00-16:00）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;欢迎体验泰式古法Massage&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;泰式&lt;b&gt;Massage&lt;/b&gt;是源远流长的传统智慧，不仅在泰国本地，也深受世界各地人们的欢迎。它能放松肌肉、促进血液循环、帮助身体恢复平衡。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;今天大家将有机会亲自感受泰式&lt;b&gt;Massage&lt;/b&gt;的魅力！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Day &lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;5&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2025-04-18 (15:00&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;–&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;16:00)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Experience Traditional Thai Massage&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Thai traditional massage is an ancient healing art widely loved in Thailand and around the world. It helps relax muscles, improve blood circulation, and restore balance to the body.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; margin-bottom:11px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-cluster&quot;&gt;Today, you’ll get the chance to experience this unique Thai therapy for yourself!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>
        </item>
